Description: KDE - language files for Portugese
License: GPL/LGPL
Maintainer: Benjamin Reed <kde-i18n-portugese@fink.racoonfink.com>

Depends: kdelibs3-unified (>= %v-11), xfonts-intl
BuildDepends: fink (>= 0.24-1), kdebase3-unified-dev (>= %v-11), kdelibs3-unified-dev (>= %v-11), libxml2, libxslt, xfonts-intl
